00:21:51.080 --> 00:21:53.359
" I was like, "Let me tell you where they are.

00:21:53.359 --> 00:21:54.779
They're all throughout Europe being trafficked.

00:21:56.020 --> 00:21:58.640
" I saw it in the spirit; it's terrible, it's sickening.

00:22:01.440 --> 00:22:01.680
And that's what the Lord said: judgment.

00:22:01.680 --> 00:22:11.240
I'm telling you folks, you're going to start seeing celebrities doing these acts, these horrendous things to these children, just fall over dead.

00:22:17.760 --> 00:22:26.583
And I saw a new venereal disease, a new venereal disease that was coming that would be worse than AIDS or any kind of herpes or anything combined, that would be not just a blood thing, but I'm talking about a terrible groin infection on men and women.

00:22:31.1000 --> 00:22:32.199
That was something out of...

00:22:34.894 --> 00:22:35.155
it looked like it was disgusting.

00:22:36.544 --> 00:22:41.326
You know, Diana and I, she's going over scriptures and going on with me and just talking about drawing close to the Father.

00:22:49.420 --> 00:22:49.590
Not saying that we're anything better.

00:22:58.426 --> 00:22:58.738
I didn't mean it like, "Well, we don't hang out with certain people.

00:22:59.360 --> 00:23:00.711
" I want to rephrase that.

00:23:00.711 --> 00:23:05.497
I was saying it like Kathryn Kuhlman kept herself separate and unto the Lord.

00:23:16.100 --> 00:23:16.360
And she said, "I don't have a social life.

00:23:16.360 --> 00:23:19.440
" And there's a lot of times whenever I realize that I complain.

00:23:19.440 --> 00:23:22.206
I said, "Lord, I like to do all this stuff.

00:23:24.250 --> 00:23:25.500
" And the Lord said, "No, I'm keeping you set apart right now.

00:23:25.500 --> 00:23:32.640
I don't want anybody influencing your mind or what I'm giving you to say.

00:23:33.600 --> 00:23:40.491
" And the more you get around other people, I realize the more God has called us to do and say these words in the end times of warnings.

00:23:40.491 --> 00:23:45.509
It's like there's some people that are called to be edifiers and they edify and they uplift.

00:23:45.509 --> 00:23:53.280
They tell everybody, "You know, you've got what it takes," but I'm here to tell you judgment's coming.

00:23:58.160 --> 00:23:59.120
And the Lord told me, the first thing he said was, "Brandon, I've called you to say the hard things.

00:23:59.120 --> 00:24:00.480
I've called Diana to say the hard things.

00:24:00.480 --> 00:24:10.880
I'm going to call you to say things that nobody else wants to say, but I want you to say it and be bold about it.

00:24:10.880 --> 00:24:18.216
And I want you to say it, and it will prove to be accurate in the days ahead.

00:24:18.216 --> 00:24:29.005
" Just because you don't see it immediately, just like Jeremiah, it didn't happen immediately, and they wanted to kill him.

00:24:41.303 --> 00:24:41.669
The Lord said that people are not going to like you for what you say.

00:24:43.360 --> 00:24:44.640
And I've seen a lot of that lately.

00:24:47.177 --> 00:24:47.394
It makes you feel very alone.

00:24:52.160 --> 00:25:14.780
And I told D, "Man, but I know I hear my Father's voice and I know what he's warning and telling me to tell the people: to get your life right, to repent, to get out of compromise, to stop having a double-standard life, thinking that you can live and you've gotten away with all this sin and you're getting away with it preaching behind the pulpit, and you're thinking you can look at porn, you think you can drink socially, and you think you can be like the world and there's no difference between you and the world.

00:25:14.780 --> 00:25:19.749
" If you had a lineup and you would say, "Who's guilty here?

00:25:39.810 --> 00:25:40.180
" and you're going through the court of law, and you say, "Who's the Christian and who's the world?

00:25:48.604 --> 00:25:49.333
" a lot of you wouldn't know because the way your wife's dressed, the way you dress, the way they carry themselves—there's no holiness.

00:25:59.484 --> 00:25:59.742
And that's what the Lord is telling me.

00:26:01.806 --> 00:26:02.011
He said, "Be ye holy as I am holy.

00:26:02.011 --> 00:26:03.039
Walk upright before me.

00:26:03.039 --> 00:26:06.456
You're the bride.

00:26:06.456 --> 00:26:07.645
Walk beside me.

00:26:07.645 --> 00:26:18.280
" Because after I gave this strong word, I was driving around the car and he gave us another word and he was talking to us.

00:26:18.280 --> 00:26:22.329
He said, "Brandon, it's like a husband that has eyes for another woman.

00:26:22.329 --> 00:26:28.400
As he's hugging onto the wife, you're looking over your shoulder looking at another girl.

00:26:28.400 --> 00:26:29.999
'Oh, I love you, babe.

00:26:29.999 --> 00:26:31.155
I love you.

00:26:31.155 --> 00:26:37.333
' But you're gazing at somebody else as they're doing whatever.

00:26:37.333 --> 00:26:41.600
" When you're walking right beside him, you don't have any eyes for somebody else.

00:26:41.600 --> 00:26:47.820
The world is not attracted to you.

00:26:47.820 --> 00:26:48.580
You're sold out.

00:26:48.580 --> 00:26:50.933
It's like me and her.

00:27:03.660 --> 00:27:03.870
I don't care—committed, we've been married for a long time, she's been through the good times, the bad times, and the middle times, whatever, but you keep working it out.

00:27:03.870 --> 00:27:05.146
That's a good marriage.

00:27:13.1000 --> 00:27:14.320
But I'm saying there is no other woman, period.

00:27:18.488 --> 00:27:21.257
You know what I'm saying?

00:27:21.531 --> 00:27:23.824
And regardless, that's the way it is with the Lord.

00:27:23.824 --> 00:27:31.235
He was talking about how our marriage is, but he was talking about how a lot of people have their backup plan, their plan B.

00:27:32.212 --> 00:27:32.408
That's what he's saying.

00:27:32.408 --> 00:27:33.800
There's a lot of plan B's.

00:27:33.800 --> 00:27:37.720
"Well, if the relationship with the Lord is not too good, it's okay.

00:27:37.720 --> 00:27:49.360
I've got a little foot over here at the world and you're floating around with a little bit of the world over here," but it's not just sold out to that individual.

00:27:49.360 --> 00:27:56.070
And that's what he was talking about: being just sold out to him.

00:27:56.070 --> 00:27:56.926
You don't have a cheating heart.

00:27:56.926 --> 00:27:59.783
Your cheating heart will tell on you.

00:28:00.926 --> 00:28:10.730
I don't know, but it's important that we are sold out to the Lord in these last days and just say, "God, I'm all in.

00:28:10.730 --> 00:28:14.040
Where are you in this end-time army?

00:28:17.510 --> 00:28:17.820
" and know that he has a plan for your life.

00:28:17.820 --> 00:28:19.946
He wants the best for you.

00:28:19.946 --> 00:28:23.199
He wants to see you whole.

00:28:23.199 --> 00:28:26.000
He wants to see you healed.

00:28:26.000 --> 00:28:30.846
It's like he told me, "Brandon, I want it more than what you do.

00:28:38.125 --> 00:28:38.399
" And I line up with what the word of God says.

00:28:42.292 --> 00:28:42.559
And he says, "By his stripes, I'm healed.

00:28:42.559 --> 00:28:43.639
" I'm healed.

00:28:43.639 --> 00:28:49.165
But I'm not going to expect God's blessing on stuff if I'm in with the world, too.

00:28:49.165 --> 00:28:55.440
"Well, you know, I give God a chance every once in a while.

00:28:55.440 --> 00:28:56.360
He's over here.

00:28:56.819 --> 00:29:07.840
" I just want him to look at me and say, "Diana, we were going over this scripture: wide is the gate.

00:29:07.840 --> 00:29:14.550
Wide is the gate and narrow is the path, and few are those that find it.

00:29:14.550 --> 00:29:16.410
What does that truly mean?

00:29:25.695 --> 00:29:25.862
" For wide is the gate and narrow is the path.

00:29:25.862 --> 00:29:26.698
Narrow is the way.

00:29:26.698 --> 00:29:27.396
Where is that?

00:29:27.396 --> 00:29:27.591
What is that?

00:29:40.133 --> 00:29:40.382
Have you ever—I mean, really think about those scriptures.

00:29:40.382 --> 00:29:44.526
'And few'—He didn't say a bunch or quite a few; He said a few.

00:29:44.526 --> 00:29:46.080
What's a few?

00:29:46.080 --> 00:29:47.502
That's like a handful.

00:29:47.502 --> 00:29:49.630
Few are those that find it.

00:29:59.240 --> 00:29:59.610
When He said, 'Depart from me, I never knew you,' those scriptures just really stand out.

00:30:07.600 --> 00:30:13.370
And those are the ones we kind of want to bypass because they're kind of uncomfortable, and you really don't know what it is.

00:30:13.370 --> 00:30:28.628
It's like, 'I don't know about that scripture,' but those two scriptures kind of go together, and you go, 'Hmm, what is He really saying there?

00:30:28.628 --> 00:30:35.449
' And that's why I thought, 'I don't want that question in my mind.

00:30:35.449 --> 00:30:39.600
All I want to know is that I am all in.

00:30:39.600 --> 00:30:48.960
' And I want you to know that you're all in today, that you're just sold out to Jesus.

00:30:52.773 --> 00:30:53.466
And that's why the Lord told me, 'Bring altar calls every single time.

00:30:53.466 --> 00:31:00.990
Bring these altar calls and pray for the people that they have a decision.

00:31:00.990 --> 00:31:08.559
' Yes, give them an opportunity to make a decision today.

00:31:19.490 --> 00:31:19.780
I thought it was interesting also that Trump said, 'I just want to make sure I go to heaven today.

00:31:19.780 --> 00:31:21.790
' I thought, 'Wow, that's amazing.

00:31:21.790 --> 00:31:30.959
' The president of the United States—it is on his heart: 'If something happens, I just want to make sure that I make heaven.

00:31:30.959 --> 00:31:32.612
' There's a stirring in him.

00:31:32.612 --> 00:31:47.946
There's a stirring in him as we're praying for his marriage, as we're praying for him to stay away from Jezebel, praying for him to stay away from this girl that will try to seduce him and be the next Marilyn Monroe.

00:31:49.012 --> 00:31:49.631
I believe he's watching these videos.

00:32:01.931 --> 00:32:02.206
I truly do, because we're praying for him, and I know that I was told Eric watches sometimes, and I think that's neat.

00:32:02.206 --> 00:32:04.240
If you're watching, Eric, hey, I'm excited you're watching.

00:32:14.373 --> 00:32:15.226
We pray for your daddy all the time.

00:32:15.226 --> 00:32:16.920
We pray for you.

00:32:16.920 --> 00:32:19.104
We pray for your brothers and sisters.

00:32:19.104 --> 00:32:21.623
We pray a covering over your family.

00:32:21.623 --> 00:32:26.617
God has a plan for you all, and I'm excited you're our first kids.

00:32:26.617 --> 00:32:30.232
What do you want to call them, the president's kids?

00:32:30.232 --> 00:32:32.400
Is that what you call them?

00:32:32.400 --> 00:32:33.679
I don't know.

00:32:33.679 --> 00:32:34.699
That sounds odd, doesn't it?

00:32:34.699 --> 00:32:35.039
'Kids.

00:32:35.039 --> 00:32:37.679
' Is that 'first lady,' 'first kids'?

00:32:37.679 --> 00:32:38.640
I don't know.

00:32:38.640 --> 00:32:39.360
First, first...

00:32:39.360 --> 00:32:40.285
it works.

00:32:40.285 --> 00:32:43.360
That's what we're going to say: they're the first kids.

00:32:43.360 --> 00:32:51.097
We're going to pray God puts a hedge around all of them, even the first grandkids.

00:32:58.800 --> 00:32:58.933
You know, it works.

00:32:58.933 --> 00:32:59.480
It's serious.

00:32:59.480 --> 00:33:05.931
But I believe God's got His hand on all the firsts, and He's got it on the seconds and the thirds.

00:33:05.931 --> 00:33:12.370
I know He has a plan for each one of us, but I know that this is not the end of the end.

00:33:13.040 --> 00:33:17.382
We're going to see a great harvest of souls, and I'm believing God for a financial harvest for our family.

00:33:17.382 --> 00:33:18.388
Big stuff.

00:33:23.664 --> 00:33:24.016
We're believing for big stuff.

00:33:24.016 --> 00:33:30.389
When you see all that we have to do, it's going to take a lot to do it.

00:33:30.937 --> 00:33:34.880
And I just keep believing that God's got this, and He has not brought us this far to fail.

00:33:34.880 --> 00:33:40.370
His hand is not short, and in all this that I keep seeing, He's going to always provide.

00:33:40.370 --> 00:33:42.746
Braden brought it up.

00:33:42.746 --> 00:33:49.950
He said, 'Daddy, do you remember when you saw the people praying around the table?

00:33:51.800 --> 00:33:52.090
There was no food in the pots.

00:33:52.090 --> 00:33:57.1000
' And there was a whole bunch of them in this time of prayer.

00:34:02.399 --> 00:34:03.777
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to supernaturally provide for My people.

00:34:09.730 --> 00:34:09.960
There will be no food in the pots.

00:34:09.960 --> 00:34:16.224
' And they set the table all around, and they'll say grace, and food will come in those pots instantaneously.

00:34:16.224 --> 00:34:18.429
Where there was no food, He will provide food.

00:34:27.420 --> 00:34:27.640
He said, 'I've never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread, regardless of what we see and what's coming in the near future.

00:34:27.640 --> 00:34:38.570
' I told somebody—I think it was Doc, this guy, his name on the chat was Doc and he was on there while we were watching—'I'm not participating in the economic disaster.

00:34:46.480 --> 00:34:46.746
I refuse to participate in it.

00:34:51.383 --> 00:34:51.691
For God gives seed to the sower and bread.

00:34:51.691 --> 00:34:55.579
' I believe He will take care of His own as we have.

00:34:55.579 --> 00:35:03.371
If you're faithful with tithing, if you're faithful in giving, if you've been faithful with little, He'll make you ruler over much.

00:35:16.440 --> 00:35:16.860
And I believe when I saw those people praying over those pots and food came in there, it wasn't just beans.

00:35:23.960 --> 00:35:24.220
It was foods like turkey, mashed potatoes, and gravy—and boom, right there.

00:35:24.740 --> 00:35:31.954
It was like all of a sudden when they prayed, the glory came into the house, filled those pots up with food, and steam was coming off the food.

00:35:35.920 --> 00:35:45.909
I saw the lady in the vision take the lid off this big pot, and there were tons of people in this house, and I saw her take the lid off, and all of a sudden, steam started coming up from this hot food.

00:35:45.909 --> 00:35:46.708
Praise God.

00:35:46.708 --> 00:35:57.422
And there was nothing in there before, and they had set it like they were having a feast, like a Thanksgiving Day feast.

00:35:57.422 --> 00:35:59.200
Candles were on there.

00:36:11.140 --> 00:36:11.330
I could see they were anticipating God to show up and show off in their life.

00:36:11.330 --> 00:36:12.720
And God did, because why?

00:36:12.720 --> 00:36:14.160
Because that's the kind of God we serve.

00:36:14.160 --> 00:36:19.086
In the middle of the night, I remember hearing...

00:36:19.086 --> 00:36:21.387
Was it George Mueller?

00:36:26.452 --> 00:36:26.675
No, not George Mueller.

00:36:31.680 --> 00:36:32.114
But there was another one I remember hearing: it was Oral Roberts.

00:36:32.114 --> 00:36:43.839
And Oral Roberts said their papa was out preaching, and there was no food in the house, and the people at the church didn't take care of them very much.

00:36:43.839 --> 00:36:47.920
They didn't have any food, and they were really, really hungry.

00:36:47.920 --> 00:36:49.691
I'm talking really hungry.

00:37:07.060 --> 00:37:07.280
And his brother was mouthing off to Oral on the way home, saying, 'God doesn't take care of us,' and just popping off.

00:37:07.280 --> 00:37:16.514
He said, 'Shut up, or I'm going to hit you in the head,' basically, because God is going to take care of us.

00:37:17.291 --> 00:37:26.627
And so they got all the way home, and he was bickering back and forth, him and his brother, because they didn't have anything to eat.

00:37:27.400 --> 00:37:33.839
And all of a sudden, Mama—because Mama said, 'I'm not going to beg for money.

00:37:33.839 --> 00:37:42.880
We're not going to do anything'—well, they got invited over to the neighbor's house, and she had all that food set out, remember?

00:37:42.880 --> 00:37:46.820
And they saw them eating the food, and Mama said, 'No, we're fine.

00:37:46.820 --> 00:37:49.850
' And he was thinking, 'No, we're not!

00:37:49.850 --> 00:37:51.140
We're starving!

00:37:51.140 --> 00:37:58.680
' They sat there and watched them because they said, 'Do you want to eat some of this?

00:37:58.680 --> 00:38:01.040
' and she said, 'No, we're okay.

00:38:01.040 --> 00:38:04.994
We're going to be just fine.

00:38:04.994 --> 00:38:08.480
God's going to take care of us.

00:38:08.480 --> 00:38:14.600
' So they went home, and what happened?

00:38:14.600 --> 00:38:16.754
Something hit their door.

00:38:16.754 --> 00:38:24.250
Somebody knocked on their door, and when they opened the door, there was all this food—all these groceries.

00:38:24.250 --> 00:38:28.160
There was a full turkey, gravy, biscuits—and it was at night.

00:38:28.160 --> 00:38:35.066
It was at night, and he said Mom went in there, and they were so hungry she made a big feast.

00:38:35.066 --> 00:38:36.819
She goes, 'Oral, go get the flour.

00:38:36.819 --> 00:38:44.780
' She got a big sack of flour, she got the eggs, and she said, 'Oral, go get the stuff out there.

00:38:54.270 --> 00:38:54.560
I'm going to make something to eat.

00:38:54.560 --> 00:38:56.480
' So they made it at night.

00:38:56.480 --> 00:39:02.342
They had a huge feast of biscuits and gravy, and they went to bed.

00:39:09.679 --> 00:39:09.959
And he told his little brother, 'I told you God would provide for us.

00:39:19.851 --> 00:39:20.286
I told you God would provide for us.

00:39:20.286 --> 00:39:23.750
' And every time I hear that, I say, 'He'll do it again and again.

00:39:23.750 --> 00:39:29.307
He'll do it again and again if you believe Him.

00:39:29.307 --> 00:39:32.320
' I'm a believing believer.

00:39:35.000 --> 00:39:35.280
I'm not a doubter.

00:39:41.840 --> 00:39:47.680
And I tell you these stories of what God is doing to inspire you to believe for your family in the days ahead, to say, 'Hey, I'm not going to participate in this.

00:39:47.680 --> 00:39:52.436
' I know what the Lord has told me is coming, ladies and gentlemen.

00:40:05.728 --> 00:40:06.072
And it will be times like we've never seen before because back then in the 1930s, people at least knew how to grow a garden.

00:40:06.072 --> 00:40:12.130
Now they don't even know how to grow some flowers, let alone a garden.

00:40:12.130 --> 00:40:12.820
It's serious.

00:40:13.280 --> 00:40:19.568
And so that's what the Lord was showing me: people don't even know how to hunt.

00:40:25.079 --> 00:40:25.339
What would you do if you shot an animal?

00:40:25.339 --> 00:40:31.960
They don't know how to even gut an animal, field dress it, and get it cleaned up.

00:40:31.960 --> 00:40:34.187
They wouldn't know what to do.

00:40:35.200 --> 00:40:35.400
That's what I'm saying.

00:40:35.400 --> 00:40:37.413
There's a lot of people who are not educated.

00:40:50.432 --> 00:40:50.720
They know a lot about computers, but they don't know about how to live.

00:40:50.720 --> 00:41:00.859
They know how to go down to McDonald's and tell them, 'I want a Happy Meal,' but they don't know how to do this.

00:41:05.143 --> 00:41:08.020
And I've seen very challenging days in the near future when this plague comes and these times come.

00:41:08.020 --> 00:41:10.266
There are hard times I've seen coming.

00:41:10.266 --> 00:41:12.400
Now, can we pray?

00:41:32.462 --> 00:41:32.693
People say that's the main thing: 'Can we pray this away?

00:41:32.693 --> 00:41:36.468
' I know that God can lessen anything, but there are parts of it...

00:41:36.468 --> 00:41:44.800
we don't want to go through hard times because we want to pass it on to the next person.

00:41:44.800 --> 00:41:49.960
But what will shake the world to bring in the harvest?

00:41:49.960 --> 00:41:58.916
That's why I said that whenever Jesus was getting ready to die on the cross, he said, 'Not my will, but yours be done.

00:41:58.916 --> 00:42:07.568
' It's not always comfortable for my flesh to go through something sometimes.

00:42:07.568 --> 00:42:15.770
Yea, though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death, I will fear no evil.

00:42:16.976 --> 00:42:18.880
He didn't say you wouldn't walk through the valley.

00:42:18.880 --> 00:42:26.862
Sometimes you walk through the valley, but we don't have to fear it.

00:42:26.862 --> 00:42:33.707
Sometimes we go through, you know, 'A thousand shall fall at our side, ten thousand at our right hand.

00:42:33.707 --> 00:42:37.920
' That means there are people dying around you.

00:42:37.920 --> 00:42:44.160
Regardless if a thousand fell around you or ten thousand at your right hand, something's going on for that to be happening.

00:42:44.533 --> 00:42:46.400
That means something was happening.

00:42:46.400 --> 00:42:47.497
Do you understand?

00:42:47.497 --> 00:42:48.045
Ten thousand, am I right?

00:42:48.045 --> 00:42:48.799
Ten thousand.

00:42:53.260 --> 00:42:53.470
I mean, seriously, that's a lot of folks.

00:42:53.470 --> 00:42:55.030
That's 11,000 people.

00:42:55.030 --> 00:42:57.280
That's a bad day.

00:42:57.280 --> 00:43:00.880
But it won't come nigh me.

00:43:00.880 --> 00:43:06.656
'Only with thine eyes shalt thou behold and see the reward of the wicked.

00:43:06.656 --> 00:43:10.062
' Father, I thank you, Lord, for Psalm 91.

00:43:20.000 --> 00:43:20.200
But even in the midst of Psalm 91, and us quoting that and believing that, there's a lot of stuff going on around us as we're saying that.

00:43:20.200 --> 00:43:23.560
It's saying that we're still protected, but man, there's still something going on.

00:43:24.960 --> 00:43:32.800
And people need to understand trying times come, but we stand by our covenant rights and we say, 'Fill the pot up, Lord.

