00:51:52.418 --> 00:51:54.089
It was terrible.

00:51:54.089 --> 00:52:03.580
How many people thought they were qualified and were ready for the rapture of the church, and they thought, 'Man, I'm just out here living a party life, but I'm saved.

00:52:12.160 --> 00:52:12.390
I love the Lord.

00:52:12.390 --> 00:52:15.700
