00:52:15.700 --> 00:52:17.954
And I saw how many people were left.

00:52:17.954 --> 00:52:37.016
There were literally tens of thousands in just one area where I was at, and they were screaming and cussing and acting out because they were left and they knew what had happened and they weren't taken and they were mad and they were flipping the Lord off.

00:52:37.016 --> 00:52:40.960
They were doing all kinds of stuff.

00:52:50.987 --> 00:52:51.520
And that shows you where their heart was right there.

00:52:51.520 --> 00:52:56.360
They weren't falling on their knees and repenting.

00:52:56.360 --> 00:53:05.839
They were acting in anger and they saw their pastors that didn't preach the truth and they were ready to hang them.

00:53:05.839 --> 00:53:07.395
Kill them right there.

00:53:07.395 --> 00:53:08.640
I saw them.

00:53:08.640 --> 00:53:10.980
There was no Holy Ghost.

00:53:24.179 --> 00:53:24.369
