00:53:24.369 --> 00:53:30.359
For the first time ever, you don't realize the prayer covering the church, the body of Christ, brings.

00:53:41.440 --> 00:53:41.771
The great restrainer—us, the church, the ones that are radical and on fire—were taken out of here.

00:53:43.760 --> 00:53:54.950
And for the first time ever, that prayer covering that was over the world that we bring every day when we do these videos and you pray in your own time, you bring a peace over the earth by your prayers.

00:53:54.950 --> 00:53:56.659
The prayers of the righteous availeth much.

00:53:56.659 --> 00:53:57.680
Remember this.

00:53:57.680 --> 00:54:07.760
Remember what I'm trying to tell you, because you still have a window of opportunity to get your heart right.

00:54:08.088 --> 00:54:15.893
I remember, and I was there, and each year the Lord took me into the years of tribulation of how bad it truly gets.

00:54:27.170 --> 00:54:27.560
And the further tribulation, the seven years—the first three and a half years was not that bad.

00:54:30.008 --> 00:54:34.107
It was terrible compared to where we are right now, but the last was unbearable.

00:54:34.107 --> 00:54:36.133
I'm talking bugs.

00:54:36.133 --> 00:54:36.480
There it was.

00:54:42.909 --> 00:54:43.139
It was awful.

00:54:47.199 --> 00:55:01.349
It looked like your worst movie you could ever think of, some kind of sci-fi, and it was like something out of that with hailstones falling out of the sky.

00:55:07.940 --> 00:55:08.200
It was awful.

00:55:08.200 --> 00:55:10.480
Do you understand?

00:55:10.480 --> 00:55:11.806
We're talking about...

00:55:11.806 --> 00:55:20.480
There was no moral law except what the Antichrist brought in to make people fear him and worship him.

00:55:28.586 --> 00:55:28.893
Everybody was acting crazy.

00:55:28.893 --> 00:55:38.480
And then when they got the chip, it made them calm.

00:55:45.307 --> 00:55:45.920
It brought a sense of peace over their minds.

00:55:45.920 --> 00:56:05.160
All of a sudden that chip comes, and they inject that chip inside of you in your forehead or your hand, and all of a sudden they go and they're like stone cold.

00:56:05.160 --> 00:56:06.559
They lose everything.

00:56:06.559 --> 00:56:07.960
I'll never forget it.

