But the people who were acting nuts, trying to pillage and stuff, the more they forced them with the drones flying in—they had drones everywhere and they watched and they let them have a chance.

00:56:25.700 --> 00:56:26.040
You take the mark, or get your head cut off.

00:56:34.880 --> 00:56:35.450
And they went and they just did it right there like a guillotine.

00:56:44.069 --> 00:56:44.377
And I saw it, and more people did not want to take that chip.

00:56:49.942 --> 00:56:50.217
When you took it, it made you a zombie.

00:56:50.217 --> 00:57:07.520
But the rioting and all the looting stopped because they had a chip in their hand and they had a chip in their forehead, and they became like a zombie, and all the looting and all the rioting and the murdering and all the craziness stopped.

00:57:18.599 --> 00:57:18.799
It did.

00:57:18.799 --> 00:57:26.079
He brought a sense of peace through a falseness through who he was, the Antichrist, over the earth.

00:57:26.079 --> 00:57:27.310
And he ruled from that place.

00:57:27.310 --> 00:57:30.525
And I watched it and everybody was like obeying little robots.

00:57:38.925 --> 00:57:39.359
But there were groups of people, pockets of people that were resistant.

00:57:48.091 --> 00:57:48.389
