00:58:27.691 --> 00:58:28.046
And they're always flying.

00:58:47.179 --> 00:58:47.389
And people think, 'Well, we'll just get away from that.

00:58:47.389 --> 00:58:50.360
' Nobody is going to hide from what I saw coming.

00:58:50.360 --> 00:58:53.474
It's not like the movies they try to make of it.

00:58:53.474 --> 00:59:01.040
No, they dug in the side of hills, in the side of the Ozarks, and in the mountains trying to hide.

00:59:01.040 --> 00:59:10.871
But the winters were so bad because the weather was so bad, with things happening with the weather, you couldn't eat.

00:59:10.871 --> 00:59:16.999
They starved to death in the side of these mountains.

00:59:16.999 --> 00:59:18.099
They starved to death.

00:59:18.099 --> 00:59:21.173
There was no water.

00:59:21.173 --> 00:59:22.729
The water was polluted.

00:59:22.729 --> 00:59:24.640
There was no way to get clean water.

00:59:28.560 --> 00:59:28.773
It was wormwood.

00:59:28.773 --> 00:59:31.599
Remember, think about what the Bible talks about wormwood.

00:59:40.391 --> 00:59:40.640
The water was bad.

00:59:41.280 --> 00:59:44.640
You couldn't drink the water; the water was making people sick.

00:59:44.640 --> 00:59:49.359
So you couldn't drink purified water; there was no way to get purifying tablets.

01:00:00.213 --> 01:00:04.480
And if you had a fire, the drones would see it and they would find you, and then they would send the authorities there and you were dead anyway.

01:00:04.480 --> 01:00:15.093
So if you don't serve Jesus now with all your heart, you're not going to serve him in the end times.

01:00:15.093 --> 01:00:19.119
All these people say, 'Well, I don't believe in the rapture.

01:00:19.119 --> 01:00:20.400
' You better.

01:00:20.400 --> 01:00:21.360
You better.

01:00:21.360 --> 01:00:22.880
That's all I've got to say.

01:00:22.880 --> 01:00:23.564
You better.

01:00:23.564 --> 01:00:26.693
All these people saying, 'Well, we're going to live.

01:00:26.693 --> 01:00:28.790
We're going to be just fine.

01:00:28.790 --> 01:00:30.740
Christians are going to...

01:00:30.740 --> 01:00:33.769
' No, they're going to die.

01:00:33.769 --> 01:00:37.354
They're going to die.

01:00:37.354 --> 01:00:46.360
Not that death is a bad thing, but I'm telling you this: I don't want nobody cutting my head off.

01:00:58.520 --> 01:00:58.789
And I don't want nobody cutting my kids' heads off.

01:01:09.679 --> 01:01:09.899
I mean, seriously, that's why I said people have no comprehension of what's about to happen.

01:01:16.994 --> 01:01:17.269
And that's just part, that's just a little bitty bit of it there.

01:01:17.269 --> 01:01:28.823
It's literal hell on earth with weather events and earthquakes and volcanoes and you name it—wars, pestilence, viruses, no medical care, hiding in the woods trying to keep your life.

01:01:28.823 --> 01:01:30.740
And that's the way it was.

01:01:34.124 --> 01:01:34.356
It was awful.

01:01:34.356 --> 01:01:39.939
Like I said, I'll never forget it.

01:01:39.939 --> 01:01:43.500
And that's why I'm so vocal and so bold about what I tell you.

01:01:43.500 --> 01:01:47.119
That's why I believe the Lord showed me this.

01:01:47.119 --> 01:01:50.529
My first major event I've had with the Father.

01:01:50.529 --> 01:01:53.516
Diana said, 'You know what's interesting?

01:02:10.950 --> 01:02:11.119
Your first major event you ever had with him was something about the end times.

01:02:11.119 --> 01:02:19.582
' And we're still talking about it all these days later.

01:02:19.582 --> 01:02:25.440
It's going on years—10 years, 11 years—warning people to get right with Jesus.

01:02:30.524 --> 01:02:31.878
And that's my whole mission, I feel like, is to pray about the end times.

01:02:40.000 --> 01:02:40.920
