01:03:40.186 --> 01:03:40.613
And I cannot even imagine approaching death without that peace that the Holy Ghost brings.

01:03:40.613 --> 01:03:52.400
So it's easy to say it now, but I cannot imagine putting my life out there without that peace.

01:04:04.639 --> 01:04:05.039
I don't want to live one second without the Holy Ghost.

01:04:05.039 --> 01:04:14.169
Just like Kathryn Kuhlman always says, 'I don't want to live one second without Him.

01:04:14.169 --> 01:04:16.360
' Yes.

01:04:16.360 --> 01:04:20.685
People have no idea.

01:04:29.419 --> 01:04:31.779
And when you don't feel that blessed assurance—you know, 'Blessed assurance, Jesus is mine'—when that's not there, it is a void.

01:04:32.890 --> 01:04:34.620
That peace that passes understanding is gone.

01:04:35.860 --> 01:04:40.709
I saw how they acted, and it was unlike any atmosphere you could ever...

01:04:51.463 --> 01:04:51.954
I felt it.

01:04:54.270 --> 01:04:55.670
I was allowed to feel what they felt.

01:04:55.670 --> 01:04:57.887
The Lord allowed me to feel it.

01:05:01.690 --> 01:05:02.000
And it's void of Him.

01:05:07.680 --> 01:05:08.080
It's void of the presence of God in the tribulation.

01:05:08.080 --> 01:05:11.735
There's nothing in people.

01:05:11.735 --> 01:05:15.988
Well, 'There's a great revival that's going to take place.

01:05:15.988 --> 01:05:19.699
' I did not see a great revival.

01:05:34.540 --> 01:05:34.730
I saw people mad and fleeing as much as they could.

01:05:41.760 --> 01:05:42.150
And they were like furious because they were still here.

01:05:42.150 --> 01:05:48.660
I don't know about you, I'm just telling y'all what I saw and what I felt.

01:05:48.660 --> 01:05:55.240
And I'm telling you, people say, 'Well, this is what the scripture says.

01:05:55.240 --> 01:05:58.640
' I'm not arguing scripture with you.

01:06:09.440 --> 01:06:09.820
There are people who believe in the tribulation, there are people who don't.

01:06:09.820 --> 01:06:11.369
I'm one that doesn't.

01:06:12.186 --> 01:06:13.089
I don't believe we're appointed unto wrath.

01:06:13.089 --> 01:06:19.554
I saw the body of Christ—the ones that were right, they shot up like rockets.

01:06:19.554 --> 01:06:20.768
They're gone.

01:06:24.079 --> 01:06:24.948
In a moment, a twinkling of an eye, we were all changed.

01:06:24.948 --> 01:06:32.730
It was that fast, so much so that it created a thunderous lightning sound when it happened.

01:06:38.480 --> 01:06:38.720
And everybody heard it.

01:06:47.200 --> 01:06:47.620
It sounded like a sonic boom, and lightning bolts were going, and the sky was alive, and it was all lightning.

01:06:52.453 --> 01:06:52.667
I remember seeing it.

01:06:52.667 --> 01:06:53.520
It was amazing.

01:06:53.520 --> 01:06:55.496
But all the kids from fifteen and younger were all gone.

01:07:04.160 --> 01:07:04.352
And those mothers—I'll never forget all those mothers—'Where's my baby?

01:07:04.352 --> 01:07:09.154
' And they were freaking out trying to find their kids because they were all gone.

01:07:09.154 --> 01:07:11.306
They all got sucked up in the rapture.

01:07:11.306 --> 01:07:13.510
They weren't appointed unto wrath.

01:07:23.039 --> 01:07:23.199
And the moms were freaking out trying to find their newborns.

01:07:26.846 --> 01:07:33.831
And that's why the Bible says, 'Woe to them who have babies,' because if they had a baby during the tribulation, it was awful because those kids suffered greatly.

01:07:33.831 --> 01:07:38.382
But if they were born before the tribulation, they were taken, and they were in the rapture.

01:07:38.382 --> 01:07:46.835
And I watched the mothers searching around, and it was all on—you know how you have missing pictures of everybody.

01:07:46.835 --> 01:07:51.550
Those missing things were on the TV, with people trying to find missing children.

01:07:51.550 --> 01:07:53.160
I'm remembering more right now.

01:08:04.091 --> 01:08:06.148
And I'm telling you, there are things I forgot, but I just saw it—the missing faces on the pictures like they used to put on the milk cartons in the old days.

01:08:07.164 --> 01:08:10.120
I don't know why that just flashed back at me.

01:08:13.960 --> 01:08:19.211
You know, there are little pieces that I'll forget, and then whenever I go, I'll remember it and it comes back just like that.

01:08:19.211 --> 01:08:20.000
It happens.

01:08:20.000 --> 01:08:21.300
It was that traumatic.

01:08:21.300 --> 01:08:26.799
I remember things, and it comes back to me about going through Guthrie and seeing those people.

01:08:40.009 --> 01:08:40.319
It's absolutely—you've never experienced fear like this.

01:08:40.319 --> 01:08:43.146
No one has the fear of feeling alone.

01:08:43.146 --> 01:08:45.111
Altar Call & Urgent Call to Salvation.

01:08:50.137 --> 01:08:50.549
The Holy Spirit brings peace, and you don't even realize it.

01:08:50.549 --> 01:08:55.260
